         <abstract id="aspace_91f6d801367b0bf63766044f1e312cbd">The collection consists of 112 glass slides which represent various aspects of African culture and scenery. The slides are identified only in broad subject areas and are undated, though most appear to date from the late nineteenth century or early twentieth century.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_0d5891d71684d297b4ab0cb05209220f">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Transferred from the African Collection curator, 1999 and 2013.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
