      <prefercite id="aspace_f189c61249d5906bdfec59d7f83577f1">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>African Glass Slides Collection (MS 1571). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_b2d0f81a592017cf03bd3cfb07369cbe">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of 112 glass slides which represent various aspects of African culture and scenery. The slides are identified only in broad subject areas and are undated, though most appear to date from the late nineteenth century or early twentieth century.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
